message.body: Not much! On Reddit after work, you?
Just out and about. Nothing special. What's Reddit? I've heard the name but don't know what it is.
It's a big forum with lots of sub-forums on different topics. There's literally a subreddit for everything, it's great for keeping up to date on stuff
Wow. Sort of like the old newsgroups but in the browser?
Haha kinda, not too familiar with those!
